The paper focuses on using deep learning methods for object detection in camera trap images, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of transfer learning, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning), and the potential for automation, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the need for data security and privacy, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
